casebody.data:
No. 1007,

Misc.

Scott, aka Plummer v. Immigration and Naturalization Service. Edward Q. Carr, Jr., for petitioner. Solicitor General Marshall for respondent.

C. A. 2d Cir. Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis and petition for writ of certiorari granted. Case transferred to appellate docket and set for oral argument immediately following No. 898.
